description:
Introducing Excitement,
a new downloadable content pack for Party Party Time!
Enjoy 10 brand-new minigames!
Join your friends and raise the roof!

The Excitement Pack includes the following content:

10 New Minigames:
6 Competitive Games
- Runaway Balls
- Dance This Way
- Stack 'n' Block
- Dodgebomb
- Sucker Punch
- Bouncing Ball Bazooka
4 Co-op Games
- UFO Collectors!
- Try-Umph
- Block Labyrinth
- Bang! Bang! Hammer
name: Excitement Pack
